	Articulate Storyline 2 First Look
	with David Rivers

	Articulate has released Storyline 2, the latest version of its
	powerful yet easy-to-use elearning software. Thinking about an
	upgrade or maybe a first-time purchase? This training course
	gives you a first look at the most important changes in
	Articulate Storyline 2, including new slider interactions,
	motion paths and triggers, and transitions and entrance/exit
	animations. Find out how to expanded support for Android
	devices and HTML5 can help make your elearning accessible on
	almost any device. Plus, learn about two of the most requested
	features: seekbars that keep learners from skipping around, and
	negative scoring, which you can use to help reinforce learning.
